snippet.title: Gas Station Story - Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Gas Station Story is a surreal sci-fi slice-of-life about love, society, and customer service -- featuring over 150 character portraits created with a Game Boy Camera! Coming to Game Boy, Windows, and MacOS in late 2024 ⛽️

Try the Demo (Web/Mobile) ⇢ https://issumatek.itch.io/gas-station-story

Wishlist on Steam ⇢ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2741780/Gas_Station_Story/

Learn More ⇢ https://www.GasStationStory.com

Music by Emberlynn Bland ⇢ https://goodnightgirl.bandcamp.com/
